job.title: UCIL Mining Mate Recruitment 2021 – Apply Offline for 51 Vacancies in Jaduguda
job.body:
Total vacancies:51

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Mining Mate

Description

New Central Government Jobs for 12th pass has been published by Uranium Corporation of India Limited for the vacancies of Mining Mate. If you are searching for a government job in Pashchimi Singhbhum, Jaduguda then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Mining Mate, from 22.05.2021, and till 09.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Pashchimi Singhbhum, Jaduguda, and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee

  • Mode of application is Offline
  • Mode of selection is Interview

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Mining Mate vacancies in Pashchimi Singhbhum, Jaduguda, your 12th must be completed by a recognized Board

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 22.05.2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is 09.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 40  years old. 

UCIL Mining Mate Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Pashchimi Singhbhum, Jaduguda Government, and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 34785.

How to apply for UCIL Mining Mate Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Mining Mate. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of UCIL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by UCIL.
  • Print out the application form
  • Fill up the details asked in the application form by blue or black pen
  • Now send this application form to the address mentioned below
  • Office of General Manager(I/P&IRs/CP), Uranium Corporation of India Limited, PO : Jaduguda Mines, Dist : East Singhbhum, Jharkhand – 832 102

Download Official notification pdf.
